    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p>\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced chicken</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 2 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1785.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1785.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1785.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
