            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1785.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>quick cook fusilli</strong> to a pot <span class=\"text-highlight\">with</span> plenty of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Cook the<strong> fusilli</strong> for just 2 min (it will keep cooking in the sauce later!)</p>\n<p>Once done, drain the <strong>fusilli</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1785.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
