            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1785.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>garlic paste</strong> to the pan with the chicken and cook for 10 sec</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> with 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and crumble in the <strong>chicken stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p>\n<p>Cook for 2 min further</p>",
